1. *Drukčije* ne mogu da zamislim tu situaciju. (*Drukčije* - differently) - I can't imagine that situation *differently*.

2. Oni gledaju *drukčije* na to pitanje. (*Drukčije* - differently) - They look at the question *differently*.

3. Bio je *drukčiji* od ostalih ljudi u toj grupi. (*Drukčiji* - different) - He was *different* from the rest of the people in that group.

4. Ova situacija je *drukčija* nego što sam očekivao. (*Drukčija* - different) - This situation is *different* than I expected.

5. Svi su tamo, osim tebe, *drukčije* je bilo planirano. (*Drukčije* - differently) - Everyone is there except for you, it was planned *differently*.

6. On je *drukčije* reagovao nego što sam očekivao. (*Drukčije* - differently) - He reacted *differently* than I expected.

7. Znam da mi je potrebno *drukčije* okruženje. (*Drukčije* - different) - I know I need a *different* environment.

8. Ova knjiga je *drukčija* od one koju sam pročitala pre. (*Drukčija* - different) - This book is *different* from the one I read before.

9. *Drukčije* bih uradio da sam bio u tvojoj situaciji. (*Drukčije* - differently) - I would have done it *differently* if I were in your situation.

10. Oni govore *drukčijim* naglaskom nego ja. (*Drukčiji* - different) - They speak with a *different* accent than I do.